    Panel
    Panel represents one electronic panel.
    PanelAscOrderNotifier
    PanelAscOrderNotifier represents a panel order notifier which dictates the billboard's panels will change color in ascending order.
    PanelColsNotifier
    PanelColsNotifier represents a panel order notifier which dictates the billboard's panels will change color in all-panels-in-column order.
    PanelOddEvenNotifier
    PanelOddEvenNotifier represents a panel order notifier which dictates the billboard's panels will change color in odd-first, even-second order.
    PanelRandOrderNotifier
    PanelRandOrderNotifier represents a panel order notifier which dictates the billboard's panels will change color in random order.
